## 1. DATA LAYER PATTERNS (src/data/notes_data.ts)

### Structure:
```typescript
// Interface definition
export interface EntryType {
  id: string;
  title: string;
  [otherFields]: PropertyType;
  createdAt: Date;
  updatedAt: Date;  // or similar timestamp field
}

// Mock data array
export const MOCK_ENTRIES: EntryType[] = [
  { id: '...', title: '...', createdAt: new Date(...), updatedAt: new Date(...) },
  // more entries
];
```

### For Reminders Data (src/data/reminders_data.ts) you'll need:
- **ReminderEntry interface**: id, title, dueDate (Date), dueTime (string), repeatOption (none/daily/weekly/monthly), notes, completed (boolean), completedAt (Date)
- **MOCK_REMINDER_ENTRIES array**: 5-10 sample reminders with varied due dates
- **Date calculations**: Use `new Date(Date.now() - 1000 * 60 * 60 * X)` to create dates relative to now
- **Sections determined at render time**: Filter entries by dueDate relative to current date

